<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.3">
<l>mātava ṉeṉṟatē koṇṭeṉṉai yiṉiyippāl paṭṭatu</l>
<l>yāta vaṅkaḷuñ cērkoṭē ṉeṉṟeṉṉuḷ pukuntiruntu</l>
<l>tītavaṅ keṭukku mamutañ centāma raikkaṭkuṉṟam</l>
<l>kōtava mileṉkaṉṉaṟ kaṭṭiyem māṉeṉ kōvintaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The ambrosia who destroys all evil,</l>
<l>having taken in [my] saying “o Mādava”, having entered into me [and] staying</l>
<l>with the words “this share has now fallen to me. I won’t betray any invitations”,</l>
	<l>a hill with red lotus eyes,</l>
<l>is my sugarcane candy without any fault, out lord, my Govinda.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
